    About this hotel

    Overlooking the Bay of Tangier, this upscale hotel with views of the Atlas mountains is 3 km from Tanger Ville train station and 6 km from the Kasbah Museum.

    The refined, warmly decorated rooms offer free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs, minibars and mountain views. Upgraded rooms feature bay views, while plush suites add living areas. Room service is available.

    Continental breakfast and parking are complimentary. There are 2 restaurants, plus an alcohol-free bar. Other amenities include beach access, a spa and a gym, as well as indoor and outdoor pools.
